<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Services</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>
<section id="services" class="bg-white pb-8" data-aos="zoom-in">
        
        <!-- judul -->
        <div class="text-center pt-10 space-y-3">
        <h2 class="font-bold tracking-wide text-3xl text-orange-600 inline-block relative">
            Layanan
            <span class="absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -bottom-3 bg-orange-400 h-0.5 w-12"></span>
        </h2>
        </div>

        <!-- deskripsi -->
         <div class="w-auto h-auto mx-auto max-w-screen-xl items-center md:py-8 py-8 px-4 sm:py-10 lg:px-6 text-gray-500 text-center">
            <p>Kami berkomitmen untuk memberikan solusi optimal dengan layanan profesional yang diberikan oleh tim kami yang berpengalaman</p>
         </div>

        <!-- container pembungkus card -->
        <div class="md:py-0 py-8 px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl sm:py-16 lg:px-6 text-gray-500 ">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-stretch "> <!-- Ganti items-center dengan items-stretch -->
                
                <!-- card 1 -->
                <div class="flex flex-col bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md shadow-gray-300 transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out hover:-translate-y-5 p-6 hover:shadow-orange-400 min-h-[100px]"> <!-- Menambahkan min-h-[100px] agar ukuran tinggi sejajar-->
                    <div class="flex items-center mb-2 space-x-3">
                        <img class="h-20 w-20" src="https://img.icons8.com/bubbles/100/wifi.png" alt="wifi"/>
                        <h5 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-orange-500">Router</h5>
                    </div>
                    <p class="mb-3 font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-500 flex-grow">Tambahkan beberapa router mikrotik dalam 1 sistem tanpa batasan</p>
                </div>

                <!-- card 2 -->
                <div class="flex flex-col bg-white shadow-md shadow-gray-300 rounded-lg transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out hover:-translate-y-5 p-6 hover:shadow-orange-400 min-h-[100px]">
                    <div class="flex items-center mb-2 space-x-3">
                        <img class="h-20 w-20" src="https://img.icons8.com/bubbles/100/workstation.png" alt="workstation"/>
                        <h5 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-orange-500">Monitoring</h5>
                    </div>
                    <p class="mb-3 font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-500 flex-grow">Monitoring Traffic, Screets Online, Screet Offline</p>
                </div>

                <!-- card 3 -->
                <div class="flex flex-col bg-white shadow-md shadow-gray-300 rounded-lg transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out hover:-translate-y-5 p-6 hover:shadow-orange-400 min-h-[100px]">
